Connectivity
============

There are many connectivity options available on the |product| industrial PC. It has |USB| (can be customized to Host or OTG), |LAN| (RJ45) Ethernet connector supporting up to
1 Gbps, and 4 x DB9 connectors.

DB9 Connectors
--------------

|Product| has 4 x DB9 connectors that are configured as RS232 by default as shown in the figure below. You can configure **COM3/COM4** as RS485. If you need different RS232/RS485 configuration, contact the Chipsee Technical Support at |email|_.

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A9/PPC_Others/DB9.jpeg
   :figclass: align-center
   :class: no-scaled-link

   DB9 Connectors
